## 13. Docker

### Dockerfile

```dockerfile
FROM python:3.11
WORKDIR /app
COPY Op_Mar /app
RUN pip install --no-cache-dir -r requirements.txt
EXPOSE 8000
CMD ["python", "manage.py", "runserver", "0.0.0.0:8000"]
